packets.name: PIXLwear P1 Sneaker “Digital Gold”, left
packets.author: Pixls
packets.description:
Bitcoin is Digital Gold and so are these sneakers. This edition is limited to only 3 issues and the sole is stamped in all gold instead of the usual PIXL brand colours, making them stand out even more when flying!

The PIXLwear P1 sneaker is a Cryptovoxels shoe for every situation. The P1 model rocks the iconic PIXLwear colours for the tie-free laces and on the sides. The insoles are stamped with “P” and “1” on the left and right shoe, respectively. This is the left shoe of the extremely limited edition “Digital Gold”. Designer: Pixls.eth. Manufactured with MagicaVoxel. PIXLwear: a PIXL brand - ethical blockchain fashion from Austria.
